Roadmap
=======
Here are the next major features that need to go into quanda,
in rough priority order. Sizes (from 1 to 5) in parenthesis.

* (2) Questions & Answers rss feed
* (2) Unanswered Questions column
* (5) Better Search
* (3) Ability to associate costs to voting up and down on questions / answers
* (3) Gravatar integration
* (5) Comments
* (4) Email notifications for answers
* (5) Twitter asking and answering capability
* (5) Badges
* (3) Sphinx documentation

